[l] Le-Monde-Ex-Korrespondentin vom Kriegsverbrechertribunal ins Gefaengnis geworfen. Und glaubt mir, die Story ist noch bizarrer als das schon vermuten laesst.The journalist Florence Hartmann, a former correspondent for Le Monde, has been jailed at the war crimes tribunal in the Hague, the body established to try the criminals she devoted her life to exposing.Die ist also eine der Guten.Hartmann was convicted for contempt of court in 2009 for revealing in a book that the tribunal had withheld crucial information on the Srebrenica massacre of 1995 from the nearby International Criminal Court. The conviction was later upheld on appeal.Wait, what?!
